name: 01. anxious.
description:
i have been searching for a medium for twenty years to get this image out of my head and into some sort of visual. 
looking at it now, after finally finding a way to make it tangible; it is beautiful. but it also leaves me breathless and terrified and anxious in a way i can not, at this moment describe. this image is the epitome of my struggle with mental health. the beginning of an incredibly long and tedious journey. this is, in a very real way, me.
